Welcome to Advanced Algebra!

I am excited to be your instructor for this course, where we will delve deeper into the fascinating world of mathematics. This class will build upon the foundational algebraic concepts you've already learned, expanding your knowledge and problem-solving skills.

Throughout the semester, we will explore various topics, including:

  • Linear equations and inequalities
  • Systems of equations and matrices
  • Quadratic functions and equations
  • Polynomial and rational functions
  • Exponential and logarithmic functions
  • Sequences and series
